                                    <div class="details">

                                        <h2>HTC One M8 Harman Kardon Edition review</h2>


                                        <div class="scorecard">

                                            <div class="left">


                                                <div class="wrap">

                                                    <h6 class="good">Highs</h6>

                                                    <ul class="good">


                                                        <li>Same great hardware as standard One M8</li>


                                                        <li>Excellent bundled headphones</li>


                                                        <li>Spotify perks (if you’re on a Framily plan)</li>


                                                    </ul>

                                                </div>



                                                <div class="wrap">

                                                    <h6 class="bad">Lows</h6>

                                                    <ul class="bad">


                                                        <li>Sprint tweaks uglify the UI</li>


                                                        <li>Still slippery in the hand</li>


                                                        <li>Competing flagships are waterproof</li>


                                                        <li>Audio tweaks have a limited appeal</li>


                                                        <li>Overloaded with pre-installed apps</li>


                                                    </ul>

                                                </div>


                                            </div>

                                            <div class="right">


                                                <div class="rating">
                                                    <div class="dt-rating num-7">Our Score<span><span>: <span>7</span></span></span>
                                                        <div class="value" style="display:none"><span class="value-title" title="7"></span></div>
                                                        <div class="best" style="display:none"><span class="value-title" title="10"></span></div>
                                                    </div>
